  My story speaks of a country  where injustice  there and the lives of many Portuguese
  citizens were in poverty ... But after Portugal turned from the kingdom to thethe
  Cloves Revolution with a revolution called the Cloves Revolution, the Portuguese
  citizen began to feel comfortable and life became more comfortable and I will speak   of
  many aspects of life when start the Republic of the development of construction
  and development in tourism and others.'
